==German==
===Etymology===
The new German army after WW2 was christened in continuity to [[Wehrmacht]], the army of the Third Reich, and the [[Reichswehr]] bevor that, but emphasizing the federal structure of post-war Germany.

===Proper noun===
'''Bundeswehr''' ''f''
# the national army of Germany
